{"tid":1251991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共政府突然忍氣吞聲意欲何在, 只係想秋後算帳咁簡單? 大家請振作","createTime":"2019-06-22T18:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T15:43:15.000Z","uid":19817,"like":235,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f4e86bc2e37ea6e40ab874fc22ffb43be64667","tid":1251991,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:24:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">港共政府由當初寸步不讓, 定性暴動, 不徹回, <br />\n去到中段改為暫緩, 但初心不變 溝通過後會進行立例<br />\n到616後依舊暫緩, 但不會重啟(所謂自然死亡, 但呢個說法並不可信, 因為佢有前科)<br />\n到左宜加開始忍氣吞聲, 打溫情牌, 但從不直接回應4大訢求(只有稍微提過徹回控罪)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">簡單黎講政府想營造一個政府係有難處唔改得字眼, 政府希望市民回歸正常生活, <br />\n心諗你中意搞就搞飽佢, 再配合TVB等媒體打輿論戰, 令民意逆轉<br />\n令示威者失民意, 令示威者鬼打鬼, 令示威者身心疲勞,  令示威者吹佢政府唔漲</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但呢D都只係表面既策略<br />\n冇錯今次示威者係有好多既進化, 但政府果邊都會一齊進化</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府心底既真正諗法係 只要今次200萬人既遊行都可以唔需要一個高官下台, 都可以唔回應訢求, 都可以足以收你地皮, 都可以送你地番歸做番個打工仔既話, 咁我之後仲洗咩怕你班港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果政府真係成功左, 佢後面既路就會好好行, 佢令到剛剛真正萌芽既呢團團結既火熄滅, 將來無論50萬,100萬和理非或者5萬,10萬既沖擊佢都可以好易就配合輿論戰處理左.<br />\n到時要再起多次火既難度係相應難好多, 250萬,300萬?  到時開始各方位打壓反對既媒體再配合每日150人令議會戰失利, 再配合各種陰質招數, 秋後算帳將所有有能力有資源既人收於牢內,<br />\n到時係咪真係咁易再起多次火? </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">所以灰心既又好, 覺得有鬼既又好, 想要大台唔想要大台又好, 想沖或者和理非都好<br />\n今場仗係唔輸得, 今場仗係我地真係第一場仗亦係最重要既一場, 我地既唯一機會, 我地一定要勝仗, 我地一定要打破呢個缺口, 我地一定要政府向市民正面回應同低頭認錯! <br />\n咁樣我地後續既真普選, 同埋基本法年期問題先可以有缺口打開!</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>振作 振作 振作</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"89021141c5d9a5b3d992a11b5bf38127dabd976d","tid":1251991,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2093696e727e84bdacff147932cf256b3106ca36","tid":1251991,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc26280adde5d4aae23aeeeba2c9320d8e60bf36","tid":1251991,"uid":514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"Well said"},{"pid":"ca56abf33f6a4bbc2e30e35d4290e23376ae30da","tid":1251991,"uid":67118,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"講得好撚中point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要港共跪低 有狗官落台"},{"pid":"5f43494941348bae7c49fa4e954cc011694e5920","tid":1251991,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30aa38689de358b0ae8efca159e01a792f9c356e","tid":1251991,"uid":212182,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:27:22.000Z","msg":"政府一定秋後算賬，需要繼續抗爭"},{"pid":"dd33d0d47846b7ca9d574205d4bd87864fb99519","tid":1251991,"uid":126704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"Well said"},{"pid":"60c63c59888687f0863ac7ce0ca7375a33a91b31","tid":1251991,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:30:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日野餐係口罩上面寫+852 抗議黑警冇number</span></span>"},{"pid":"4fd0dd569e242aa5f507b58388c642a9676bbd4e","tid":1251991,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc3435ae091bf21c6f767dd8d8219fa9c7d8753","tid":1251991,"uid":191309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:34:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d08db5608b020d77175ccf31a5a49cb67d67f7f","tid":1251991,"uid":231040,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQXj8Ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQXj8Ad.jpg&h=cd49b3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家經歷過這兩星期的抗爭運動都辛苦了! 雖然「五大訴求」(包括埋「林鄭下台」)仍然未達到，但希望大家趁呢兩日先好好地休息，之後重新裝備再齊齊繼續抗爭吧~<br />\n<br />\n不過，有啲事就真係比較急嘅，就係 - <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">距離今屆新選民登記嘅截止日期<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>仲剩番10日咋</strong></span>!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你自己、兄弟姐妹、同事朋友等等仲未登記嘅，請好好把握今次嘅機會立即登記，以便喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">今年24/11嘅區議會選舉</span></ins></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: pink;\">出年立法會選舉</span></ins></strong></span>，將一個一個賣港又冇立場嘅親共政棍跟尾狗狠狠地踢出議會，將議會嘅否決權還番俾人民吧!!!<br />\n(可惜嘅係，已登記選民嘅更改資料期限已經喺2/6結束了，但大家仍需要覆查自己嘅選民資料有冇俾人更改／刪除咗，尤其係最近換咗新身分證嘅朋友)<br />\n<br />\n有關選民登記嘅資料如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">《地方選區選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=51b9e609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">《功能界別選民及／或選舉委員會界別分組選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=302fa118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">網上更新電郵地址</span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk%2Fosp%2Fra008%2FmainEM.jsp%E2%80%A6&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=98ee09e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">選民資料網上查閱系統</span></span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=4b852923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n此外，資料組嘅朋友可以好好地利用呢段時間，儲齊呢段時間來班建制狗所做嘅「好人好事」並作出整理，成為「彈藥」以供文宣組嘅朋友製作長輩圖及其他文案等，對一眾被利用嘅中年／老人家作出「反洗腦」宣傳，辛苦大家了！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>＊＊＊ <span style=\"color: pink;\">齊心登記</span>，<span style=\"color: pink;\">一齊投票</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">用選票拆散保皇狗</span> ＊＊＊</strong></span>"},{"pid":"dfc818673d37d32784602b3de955bf6ebdeed314","tid":1251991,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed466a9f69f73ed443271df5f481a9083e6d68df","tid":1251991,"uid":93350,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"repl